{
  "stem": "3988.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sisters, you know, my family, they shipped them out to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's the one who escaped, or he wasn't there at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's the one that come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He told me, you know, they were shipped out to Auschwitz, you know, and everything, and what happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All my parents, you know, my sisters, whole family, I'm the only one-- I made it-- you know, perished in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from my family, I'm the only one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not nobody.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm the only one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had an uncle and aunt in Denmark and cousins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had an uncle here in the United States, you know, cousins, and the other thing, which they left for Poland, the First World War, before First World War.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's where they stayed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, when I went, and they took me away from my parents, you know, when they took me into camps, my mother gave me two addresses to take with me, address from my uncle from the United States, and address in Denmark.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had those addresses up to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, in the civilian camps-- in civilian camps, when I was there, I could keep, you know, things with me, pictures, or anything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when I came to Auschwitz, you know, I was stripped of everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they gave you that uniform, that stripped uniform, that was it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when I was in-- in the DP camp after the war, you know, people start finding out, and writing, you know, I'll see you, and another thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and I believe Red Cross came in our camp and wanted to know, you know, we have any relatives some place, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, you know, they send away information.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember the-- the address from Denmark.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
